title: SKIP HOP BANDANA BUDDIES UNICORN ACTIVITY TOY
description: A perfect introduction to multi-sensory play for baby, this soft animal activity toy is one part teether, one part plush toy and totally entertaining. Featuring rattles, crinkle sounds and multiple textures for baby to explore, it’s the perfect playtime friend to keep baby busy and happy—at home or on-the-go. From our elephant toy and unicorn to more cute critters, you’re sure to find an animal your little one will love.

title: BUMBO BABY INFANT TODDLER SOFT FOAM MULTI SEAT WITH REMOVABLE TRAY AND SAFETY BUCKLE STRAPS FOR KIDS` 6-36M
description: For the Ultimate Three Stage Seat Bumbo introduces the Bumbo Multi Seat, the next step in seating for your child. This 3-in-1 seat functions as a Floor Seat, Booster Seat and Feeding Seat. The Bumbo Multi Seat is ideal for babies who have already mastered the Bumbo Floor Seat and will see your child through to the toddler stage with a seat that grows with your child. With attachment straps to easily convert from a floor seat to a booster seat, you can begin enjoying key developmental milestones from feeding to playtime as soon as your child can begin to sit unassisted. The seat's foam pad cushions your baby and can be removed to create more room as they grow. The removable tray attaches to the back of the Multi Seat for easy storage and transport. Recommended for ages 6 months  - 36 months.

title: WINFUN LAPTOP JUNIOR - TIGER
WINFUN LAPTOP JUNIOR - TIGER
FISHER-PRICE SANRIO HELLO KITTY BABY MUSICAL GYM
description: Baby can hang out with Hello Kitty and friends at the Sanrio Baby Musical Gym from Fisher-Price®! This activity gym features a machine-washable playmat and 5 repositionable toys including a self-discovery mirror, a strawberry rattle, a BPA-free leaf teether, a crinkle book, and a Hello Kitty plush that plays 20 minutes of music. All that reaching and grasping for toys and tummy-time play helps develop hand-eye coordination and neck and core strength.

title: TINY LOVE TINY ROCKERS ELECTRONIC ACCORDION BABY LEARNING TOY
description:
Tiny Love’s unique developmental system focuses on 6 essential skills — emotions, creativity, motor skills, senses, cognition, and communication. Created with love and care by our child developmental experts, the system supports a baby’s journey of exploration from one developmental milestone to the next, encouraging parents to explore alongside their little ones.



The Tiny Rockers Accordion from Tiny Love boasts engaging features that are fun to play with while focusing on the development of your child’s motor skills, senses, creativity, and cognition while enjoying a song, dance, and big smile together. Every part of it is designed to not only stimulate their attention but to nurture it. You can choose between 7 different pre-loaded rock n’ roll melodies to listen to or use the mode selector to let your child play a song of their own. Freedom of play inspires your child to express their creativity. Two easy-to-hold grip handles make it easier for your child to enjoy making music just like a real accordion! A pitch slider adds to the sonic fun. Each of the 7 piano keys carries its own tune, changing between classic or electric sounds with the flip of a switch. 4 fun LED lights help distinguish the keys from one another and keep the music flowing. Rocking and rolling into a groovy world of development and fun with Tiny Love.

title: TINY LOVE MAGICAL TALES™ MAGICAL NIGHT 3-IN-1 PROJECTOR MOBILE
description: The Magical Night Mobile 3-in-1 Projector Mobile and starry night lamp is the perfect sleepy time companion for your little one. Your baby will enjoy viewing the mobile projection on the overhead canopy, following the playful animals’ movements. Your little one will be delighted by the wonderful array of stars that project onto the ceiling. It also converts into a music box with 3 different musical categories and 9 tunes, with up to 30 minutes of continuous runtime. The soothing music encourages cognition, while the cute, smiling characters develop language and communication. This adorable nighttime companion is a wonderful way to make bedtime more fun for everyone.
